Package: linux-headers-st1-5
Architecture: armel
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-headers-${kernel-abi-version}-st1-5
Description: Linux kernel headers -- st1-5
 This package will always depend on the latest st1-5 kernel headers
 available.

Package: linux-image-st1-5
Architecture: armel
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-${kernel-abi-version}-st1-5, linux-firmware
Description: Linux kernel image -- st1-5
 This package will always depend on the latest st1-5 kernel image
 available.

Package: linux-st1-5
Architecture: armel
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-st1-5 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Complete Linux kernel -- st1-5
 This package will always depend on the latest complete st1-5 Linux kernel
 available.

